                        android:paddingLeft="20dp"
                        android:paddingRight="20dp"
                        android:textSize="18sp"
                        android:text="Cool the burn with cool or lukewarm running water for 20 minutes as soon as possible after the injury. Never use ice, iced water, or any creams or greasy substances like butter."
